trans-unit.source: Manages user interface in the designer.
trans-unit.target: Hanterar användargränssnittet i designern.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: When the BehaviorService is created, it adds a transparent window over the designer frame.
trans-unit.target: När BehaviorService skapas, lägger till ett transparent fönster över designer ramen.

trans-unit.source: The BehaviorService can then use this window to render user interface elements, called <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph> objects, as well as catch all mouse messages.
trans-unit.target: BehaviorService kan sedan använda det här fönstret ska renderas gränssnittselement, kallas <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph>objekt, samt generell musen meddelanden.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph>

trans-unit.source: In this way, the BehaviorService can control designer behavior.
trans-unit.target: På så sätt kan kan BehaviorService styra designer.

trans-unit.source: The BehaviorService class supports a behavior stack, onto which <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Behavior> objects can be pushed.
trans-unit.target: Klassen BehaviorService stöder ett beteende-stacken, där <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Behavior>objekt kan skickas.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Behavior>

trans-unit.source: When a message is intercepted through the transparent window, the BehaviorService can send the message to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Behavior> at the top of the stack.
trans-unit.target: När ett meddelande fångas via fönstret transparent BehaviorService kan skicka meddelandet till den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Behavior>överst i stacken.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Behavior>

trans-unit.source: This enables different user interface modes depending on the currently pushed <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Behavior>.
trans-unit.target: Detta gör att olika användare gränssnittet läge beroende på den för närvarande intryckt <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Behavior>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Behavior>

trans-unit.source: The BehaviorService is used to render all <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph> objects, such as selection borders, sizing handles, and smart tags.
trans-unit.target: BehaviorService används för att återge alla <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph>objekt, till exempel markeringen kantlinjer storlekshandtag och smarta etiketter.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph>

trans-unit.source: The BehaviorService also controls many design-time behaviors, such as using snaplines, dragging, and selecting.
trans-unit.target: BehaviorService kontrollerar även många designläge beteenden, till exempel med hjälp av snaplines, dra och markera.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Behavior Service Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [översikt över beteendet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.
trans-unit.target: Anropa Dispose när du är klar med hjälp av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Dispose lämnar den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>oanvändbar.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: När du anropar Dispose, måste du släppa alla referenser till den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>så skräpinsamlingen kan frigöra minne som den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>var upptar.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) och [implementera en metod för ta bort](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid anropet avyttra innan du släpper senaste referens till <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: De resurser som den använder frigörs annars inte förrän skräpinsamlingen anrop av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>objektets `Finalize` metod.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>
